{"tid":2215974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[有圖] 其實目前為止，你地知唔知內蒙個邊發生咩事？今日內蒙，明日香港","createTime":"2020-09-24T10:42:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T15:12:08.000Z","uid":188515,"like":54,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"6274ab69381e3c0382698c91fd2f7d5e70bb86f7","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:42:56.000Z","msg":"語言，作為一個族群既溝通工具  <br />\n同時象徵著身份既建構<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n若果族群既語言瓦解<br />\n背後承載既文化與歷史記憶亦會消亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而呢個族群亦會逐漸俾人同化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TnkLNfp.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTnkLNfp.gif&h=7016ba7b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而中国既蒙古人亦正正面對呢種情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係8月個陣中国已經要求中、小學<br />\n逐步改用普通話教書，用簡體字既教材<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XQJ9vv5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXQJ9vv5.jpg&h=a940b716&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但由於內蒙係全球唯一保留傳統蒙文既地方<br />\n亦因為咁，當地即刻係8月尾開始示威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8whN1C0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8whN1C0.jpg&h=45353920&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而中国亦派出大量黑警鎮壓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FzRnQv6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFzRnQv6.jpg&h=28416643&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n禁錮學生係學生，阻止佢地罷課<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nep8L4u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnep8L4u.jpg&h=a42cc595&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以「尋釁滋事」既罪名通緝示威者<br />\n公開佢地既身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q6haZpv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ6haZpv.jpg&h=c388b28c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n封哂所有有關示威既消息<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1H63zXR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1H63zXR.jpg&h=f197efa1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n威脅蒙人要送仔女返學，如果唔係「後果自負」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z3zQeXT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz3zQeXT.jpg&h=8f30e6f0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n甚至直接埋你屋企，同佢地「深入訪談」<br />\n勸你唔好周圍走，會好危險咖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P4GbJRe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FP4GbJRe.jpg&h=b401d93c&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後華大媽個堆亦將呢場示威<br />\n定性為境外煽動、分裂國家的活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n強調會依法嚴厲執法<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zbm7hg0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZbm7hg0.jpg&h=067e0226&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇到呢到，係咪覺得好似香港咁？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你地一定會話，應該係「昨日香港，今日內蒙」<br />\n<br />\n但從教育既角度睇，香港依然未好似內蒙咁<br />\n但其實已經不斷咁滲透緊我地既語言同文化<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jM2ycKC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjM2ycKC.jpg&h=4d8d33f5&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我地既下一代可能開始正係用普通話<br />\n正係寫殘體字 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rOcBUXZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrOcBUXZ.jpg&h=47fbd814&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但其實，如果一個地方既人<br />\n連自己最引以為傲既語言都無辦法保存既話 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲點樣去捍衛佢地既文化同核心價值？<br />\n有時與其坐以待斃，倒不如坐言起行<br />\n用行動証明自己捍衛母語既決心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n將我地既語言同文化繼續咁傳承落去 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cWxVq4H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcWxVq4H.jpg&h=f398694e&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n以下係洛杉磯時報對當地示威既深入分析<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.co/sGMEldTwld\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FsGMEldTwld&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=0883cfa2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.co/sGMEldTwld</a><br />\n<br />\n另外，呢條片會講得再詳細啲當地既情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n鍾意既可訂閱手足，個channel講歷史同電影野多（代post）<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VYDeVippl_c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVYDeVippl_c&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=af0fbfb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VYDeVippl_c</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當地既消息已經愈嚟愈少<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n據聞好多人寧死不屈，有啲就係屋企教自己既仔女<br />\n有啲仲要走左入大草原避開中共<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以請大家繼續到twitter關注事件<br />\n<br />\n「今日內蒙，明日香港」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6dc6e4b8cbe443ad371c3fc4bf34707bdf6e808","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:44:01.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a408d47f6ffc588844f698d3a6ad691df44565f3","tid":2215974,"uid":44209,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"您喜歡用「南蒙古」，而不喜歡用「內蒙古」，為什麼？<br />\n<br />\n因為「內」蒙古是中國人自己編出來的，非常具有宣傳色彩，是非常漢化的一個詞，目的是對這個地區提出領土主張。在我們自己的語言裡，我們稱自己為「Uvur Mongols」，意思是「南蒙古」或「蒙古南部」。蒙古語「Uvur」一詞根本沒有「內」的意思。"},{"pid":"e87b94e9a2830f6cff827105e0090ff8e3f86a34","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:45:56.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VYDeVippl_c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVYDeVippl_c&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=af0fbfb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VYDeVippl_c</a>"},{"pid":"2e70202c27f79f05e6941fb4ae620cf6c61bc544","tid":2215974,"uid":4396,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:46:04.000Z","msg":"其實而家已經係普通話教學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />現實就係咁，短時間內都做唔到啲咩<br />\n所以一定要打好國際線"},{"pid":"bf2a0ccf2d4e5f810c90dfa356690aaef2c6c15f","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a408d47f6ffc588844f698d3a6ad691df44565f3","tid":2215974,"uid":44209,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:45:13.000Z","msg":"您喜歡用「南蒙古」，而不喜歡用「內蒙古」，為什麼？<br />\n<br />\n因為「內」蒙古是中國人自己編出來的，非常具有宣傳色彩，是非常漢化的一個詞，目的是對這個地區提出領土主張。在我們自己的語言裡，我們稱自己為「Uvur Mongols」，意思是「南蒙古」或「蒙古南部」。蒙古語「Uvur」一詞根本沒有「內」的意思。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:47:23.000Z","msg":"絕對明白呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之前啲post都講過有原因的，但唔係到解釋"},{"pid":"3f459965784343445388965098e785898b6de64e","tid":2215974,"uid":89681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"&quot;但由於內蒙係全球唯一保留傳統蒙文既地方&quot;<br />\n好奇一問 咁蒙古用咩文？"},{"pid":"da1ea57d3e888d72cfa6d71f64d3560e38fe32b8","tid":2215974,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:47:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b7b0a8fd94612a364f773f42e984afa7a40dba2","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"3f459965784343445388965098e785898b6de64e","tid":2215974,"uid":89681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"&quot;但由於內蒙係全球唯一保留傳統蒙文既地方&quot;<br />\n好奇一問 咁蒙古用咩文？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:48:42.000Z","msg":"蒙古國依加係用緊西里爾字母改出嚟既蒙古文<br />\n已經無哂自己既文化內涵<br />\n詳情可以睇片"},{"pid":"e4232d6dc4e9f6ff582f86eee28becc912ef42aa","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:49:37.000Z","msg":"「今日內蒙，明日香港」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VYDeVippl_c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVYDeVippl_c&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=af0fbfb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VYDeVippl_c</a>"},{"pid":"7027aa709fd8ebba239ad8480c66b87669a3cccf","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:50:10.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8c425cb0c8a7b5c17b23b085de1d817639fb4869","tid":2215974,"uid":282637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:50:58.000Z","msg":"有線條link?<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24fc63fb575f65366b25e1e89cb4a13c505adfeb","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:53:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"828aa1b1e683be5079fbfcfcd24166d84e3d9898","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:54:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"21753deab25cff171292430ed3be1262c9b57759","tid":2215974,"uid":114074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:56:22.000Z","msg":"而家香港應該都接近半個內蒙<br />\n過多幾年...唉"},{"pid":"7722b5f016daad464177c7797fd364568f0517f3","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:00:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94b6b661b10196188778ff93a4e0294123634726","tid":2215974,"uid":85311,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:03:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3592828ecc0f06ed7b4601d417f1c1f171248f85","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:22:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"480a9adc92fe1177c84e034f146dbd5fee4870f7","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:24:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"84c59a2b816fc695b3aef66314092046120fec24","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:25:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bfd5c74ce2e722b502b87a76d32e8b71233fd4e8","tid":2215974,"uid":91397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:27:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32bb42510c6499c51f08b187561701d31930db12","tid":2215974,"uid":92448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:27:24.000Z","msg":"天滅支那"},{"pid":"35d86a748e323834c3af7b5fbcf0fa28ace82221","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:44:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d4a0586e3284f623dfa0abf89cc26dd50725022e","tid":2215974,"uid":491,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:47:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2492715bbd9f18fceb68383fa9c050907f55b34a","tid":2215974,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T11:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"e4232d6dc4e9f6ff582f86eee28becc912ef42aa","tid":2215974,"uid":188515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T10:49:37.000Z","msg":"「今日內蒙，明日香港」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VYDeVippl_c\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DVYDeVippl_c&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=af0fbfb9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VYDeVippl_c</a>"}}